miso.carrascal.cloudModelServices.abstractServices

Interface InterfaceDB

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MongoDB

    public interface InterfaceDB
    Interface for all databases. Important information: The keys for the objects are {id, classType} or their filenames. An id alone can be repeated, but an artifact with same id and classType, or with same filename are prohibited.
    Author:
    Carlos Carrascal
